descriptor.name: Prestige PWG 07 Wet Grinder with Stainless Steel Drum 200 W, 2 L (Black, Orange)
descriptor.short_desc: Prestige PWG 07 Wet Grinder with Stainless Steel Drum 200 W, 2 L (Black, Orange)
descriptor.long_desc: Grind batter for crispy dosas, soft idlis or fluffy vadas. Manufactured with highest quality materials, Prestige Wet Grinder is designed specially to handle your wet grinding jobs effortlessly, making it a truly versatile companion for you in your kitchen. It's Quicker: The uniquely designed grinding stone with larger contact area supported by heavy-duty motor, ensures quicker grinding. It's Quieter: The advanced interlocking mechanism ensures proper alignment of the roller shaft. reducing noise while grinding.

descriptor.name: Prestige PIC 29.0 Induction Cooktop 2000 W with Pre-set Indian Menu Options (Orange)
descriptor.short_desc: Prestige PIC 29.0 Induction Cooktop 2000 W with Pre-set Indian Menu Options (Orange)
descriptor.long_desc: Prestige brings you the exquisitely designed Induction cooktop which is an amazing combination of performance and beautiful aesthetics. Add convenience and color to your kitchen in one go with the new Prestige Induction Cooktop. With striking blue exterior and versatile functionality tuned perfectly for the Indian kitchen, these cooktops have various Indian menu options available to enjoy your favorite delicacies. It’s environment friendly design does not consume much electricity and hence it saves energy. Also, it is specially designed with Insect proof coating that ensures hygiene. All-in-all, it’s the perfect cooking companion you’ve been waiting for.

descriptor.name: Prestige CleanHome PCIL 4 Steps Household Ladder (Orange, Silver)
descriptor.short_desc: Prestige CleanHome PCIL 4 Steps Household Ladder (Orange, Silver)
descriptor.long_desc: Be it for changing a bulb, fixing the gallery lights, or cleaning, Prestige brings to you a supremely functional ladder which lets you do all the household chores with ease. With anti-skid steps and rubber grip, this ladder offers a hassle-free day-to-day experience, and that too, with utmost safety. So, go ahead and bring home a perfect companion for all your chores.
